data.description:
MASSIVE PRICE REDUCTION!! MOTIVATED SELLER!Nestled in the charming community of Crestview, Florida, this exquisite residence at 2970 Stillwell Boulevard offers a harmonious blend of modern comfort and timeless elegance. With its thoughtfully designed interior spaces, impressive amenities, and convenient location, this property presents a truly exceptional living experience.This well-appointed home  maximizes both space and functionality. From the moment you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting foyer that flows seamlessly into the various living areas.The heart of the home is the kitchen, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, ample counter space, and tons of potential. This kitchen would be perfect paired with an island The property offers a collection of well-proportioned bedrooms, including a master suite designed as a private oasis. With high ceilings, large windows, and lavish ensuite bathrooms, these bedrooms provide a restful retreat.

From the cozy family room to the elegant formal dining area, this home provides a range of spaces to entertain and enjoy time with family and friends. The open-concept design encourages a natural flow between indoor and outdoor entertaining areas.

Step outside to discover an outdoor haven that features a covered patio, perfect for alfresco dining or lounging. The well-landscaped yard offers ample space for outdoor activities and gardening.

Equipped with modern amenities such as smart home features, energy-efficient appliances, and updated HVAC systems, this home effortlessly combines convenience with contemporary living.

Situated in central Crestview, this property enjoys the advantages of a desirable neighborhood while still being close to shopping and restaurants. Residents have easy access to local schools, parks, shopping centers, and major roadways, making daily commutes and errands a breeze.

2970 Stillwell Boulevard presents a unique opportunity to acquire a stunning home that harmonizes style, comfort, and functionality. With its array of features and prime location, this property invites you to experience the finest in Florida living. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional residence your own and create lasting memories for years to come. (Seller has survey)
